cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image classification and clustering, which are primarily computer vision tasks (cs.CV). The method proposed in the paper involves learning a new image representation, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of prototypes and similarities, which are concepts commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.LG, and cs.AI, followed by cs.CL and cs.MM.
